Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.54,0:00:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,補習到今天為止就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.56,0:00:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.20,0:00:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝老師
