Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.80,0:00:36.00,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸の奥が高鳴る
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.90,0:00:39.60,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱い声に気づいたら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.74,0:00:41.72,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,スタートラインは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.47,0:00:44.98,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君の目の前にある
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:47.43,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まだ見えない道でも
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.05,0:00:51.03,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走り始めればいいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.08,0:00:53.12,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諦めるよりも
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.82,0:00:56.42,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,素敵だと思わない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.69,0:01:01.43,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつも不安はすぐ傍で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:07.41,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駆け出す思いを　締め付けるけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:10.60,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今を越えて　歩き出す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:13.27,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未知なる道に光を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:16.39,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初めてを　繰り返し
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.52,0:01:18.94,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掴み取れ　明日を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.97,0:01:22.13,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そうさ友達が無限の
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.18,0:01:24.70,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢抱きしめ　進むのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.86,0:01:30.83,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輝いてる自分を信じていい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:33.58,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立ち上がる力に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.67,0:01:36.34,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大の愛をこめて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.49,0:01:39.11,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思うまま　変えた今日を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.13,0:01:45.16,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新しい世界乗り変え
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.80,0:00:36.00,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開歌喉 高聲歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.90,0:00:39.60,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望有人能注意到自己熱情的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.74,0:00:41.72,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生的起跑線
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.47,0:00:44.98,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在你的眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:47.43,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然前邊的路看不到盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.05,0:00:51.03,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇敢的朝前走就行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.08,0:00:53.12,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.82,0:00:56.42,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不是更好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.69,0:01:01.43,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不安一直徘徊在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:07.41,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就將自己這份雀躍的心情小心收起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:10.60,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來邁出自己的腳步 超越現在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:13.27,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照亮前方那條未知的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:16.39,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成一個又一個目標
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.52,0:01:18.94,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用自己的雙手緊緊抓住未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.97,0:01:22.13,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友們快來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.18,0:01:24.70,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們一起擁抱無限的夢想 朝前進發
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.86,0:01:30.83,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信閃閃發亮的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:33.58,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振奮人心的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.67,0:01:36.34,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飽含著滿滿的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.49,0:01:39.11,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣 改變今天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.13,0:01:45.16,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們一起擁抱新的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.98,0:01:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中同學發這個音吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.75,0:02:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(發聲練習)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.21,0:02:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起 來！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.04,0:02:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起練習真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.48,0:02:36.60,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad3\4c&HA6A4A5&\bord0\fad(400,200)}第七話  {\bord2\4c&HA1D734&} {\4c&HD7EEA6&\3c&HFBFEF0&\c&H8473F7&}時而空忙 {\c&HE3A37C&\4c&H8973F9&} 時而迷失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.79,0:02:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}合唱·有時打打羽毛球部會議
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.79,0:02:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}今天的議題 關於白祭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.50,0:02:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 首先
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.37,0:02:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有請成為正式成員的阪井和奏跟大家打個招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.15,0:02:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？ 我沒聽過有這一套啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.40,0:02:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪井 請起立
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.44,0:02:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.41,0:02:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.29,0:02:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和奏加油
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.12,0:02:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 說什麼好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.58,0:02:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.77,0:03:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,額…我是重新加入合唱部的阪井和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.28,0:03:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前沒有好好參加活動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.47,0:03:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對大家的態度也不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一本正經的問候就到此結束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啦 和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上開始討論白祭的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.90,0:03:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請說 維也納同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.42,0:03:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白祭是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.12,0:03:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這問題開始啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.26,0:03:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,——文化節哦             ——白色的犀牛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.26,0:03:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}犀牛和祭在日語裏發音相同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.32,0:03:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是白色的犀牛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.07,0:03:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種犀牛？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.30,0:03:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長著角的那種嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.19,0:03:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 你應該知道體育館的地下有著白色的犀牛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？ 在地下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們每年把那頭犀牛牽出來一次 來慶祝節日哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊行啊 唱歌跳舞啊什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.55,0:03:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是 一直被困在地下就太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.93,0:04:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今合唱部就來討論下節日那一天我們能舉行什麼樣的活動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家踴躍提出自己的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.86,0:04:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.54,0:04:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生還真是可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.87,0:04:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.49,0:04:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您收好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.83,0:04:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}騎馬教室 羽毛球教室 貓咪咖啡廳 英雄形象秀 吃貨大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和唱歌一點關係都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.97,0:04:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就唱歌騎馬教室
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.89,0:04:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱歌羽毛球
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.16,0:04:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱唱英雄秀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌唱貓咪咖啡屋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱歌吃貨大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.00,0:04:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.23,0:04:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為體育館有個舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.44,0:04:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以會有很多觀眾聚集到體育館
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.17,0:04:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們第一次也是最後一次的大舞台哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.32,0:04:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犀牛也會來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.83,0:04:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犀牛就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.40,0:04:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通的合唱不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.76,0:05:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…這樣的話肯定會輸給聲樂部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.67,0:05:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然合唱的話還是人多比較有魄力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不想輸給教導主任啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.21,0:05:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那歌劇怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.98,0:05:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5個人演歌劇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.05,0:05:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我們一般只是唱唱歌 壓根就沒練過歌劇…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意輸贏 唱出我們自己的歌不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.03,0:05:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真帥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.45,0:05:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 本來就是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.61,0:05:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是 那就先這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.84,0:05:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教導主任和聲樂部啥的都是小菜一碟啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.72,0:05:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 聲樂部的上野和部長廣畑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}這本是不是太簡單了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}嗯 但是我還是要這本
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.68,0:06:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了可以一起開心玩樂的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.88,0:06:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲樂部的同學都是在為未來打算認真而參加活動的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要不老過來打擾的話我就很高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.54,0:06:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見（ciao） 噪音（strepitoso）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.66,0:06:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Strepitoso？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.52,0:06:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘈雜的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Strepitoso是音樂用語
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘈雜的 吵鬧的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.07,0:06:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘈雜就嘈雜唄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.05,0:06:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不想輸給她們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.32,0:06:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就先去學生會室啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再會 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去進行騎射訓練 先回去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}註：原文為「流鏑馬」日本鐮倉時代的武藝之一 射手邊策馬奔馳邊依次射擊在三個地方的靶子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.48,0:06:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從今天開始也要去上補習班了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:06:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,補習班？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.12,0:07:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是高考生了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.89,0:07:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中同學不是體育特長生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是體育特長生 也不知道能不能考上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.62,0:07:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦落榜 就不能打羽毛球了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.59,0:07:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.63,0:07:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都有為未來做打算呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.53,0:07:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和奏準備怎麼辦呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.93,0:07:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒想好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.31,0:07:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們倆還真相像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在有想要實現的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.86,0:07:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先從它開始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.07,0:07:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去趟圖書館就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.06,0:07:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小誠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.31,0:07:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在看什麼 H書？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.64,0:07:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來申請文化祭主舞台的名額的說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.86,0:08:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生會的副書記還真是閒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.45,0:08:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 趕緊填好了就出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯… 演出內容
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.78,0:08:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就暫時填個「又唱又跳」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐 你以為這個名額隨隨便便就能拿得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.17,0:08:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？ 難道不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.01,0:08:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於每年有許多申請名額的優秀個人及團體
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以每次都會舉辦選拔賽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.01,0:08:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這不涉及正式成立的社團啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.39,0:08:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,截止到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.05,0:08:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,申請名額的可儘是聲樂部啊吹奏樂部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些超有實力的社團哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.71,0:08:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負責安排主舞台的可是教導主任哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.82,0:08:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.53,0:08:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩布萊 星期天再一起訓練哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.93,0:09:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢業後或許就要和你分開了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.23,0:09:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然擅自拆看了我的信 真是難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過很多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騎馬只能當成一種消遣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.18,0:09:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有考慮過一旦失敗的後果嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並非只靠努力就能當上的職業騎手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.53,0:09:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是女性…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.75,0:09:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽馬什麼的不就是賭博嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是叫你完全放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.13,0:09:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當個公務員什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找份正經工作 把騎馬當成興趣就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟爸爸你已經沒什麼好說的了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:09:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那錢要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有在打工存錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.50,0:10:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然現在還不多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.40,0:10:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不夠的那部分怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.43,0:10:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.99,0:10:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的衣食學費
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.70,0:10:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是靠工作賺錢得來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.55,0:10:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過工作養活一家人 這才是職業
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.93,0:10:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所謂的騎馬不是職業
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是消遣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這叫什麼話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒求你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就還你好了 這些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.29,0:10:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我賣了拿了錢還你總行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.49,0:10:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 別這樣 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很熱鬧嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.29,0:10:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以換種好聽點的說法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.55,0:10:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有勝負的世界 可不像你想像的那麼輕鬆哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.01,0:10:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.73,0:10:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禿頭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.37,0:10:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.06,0:10:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說你禿頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:10:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}志願調查表
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.99,0:11:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致親愛的小楊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.12,0:11:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合唱部的夥伴們都朝著各自的目標努力著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.09,0:11:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這明明是件非常好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我的心情卻十分浮躁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.37,0:11:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候才能找到我的目標呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.93,0:12:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟…我從何而來 又將去往何處
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.42,0:12:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我不能這麼消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.35,0:12:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天聽說了一件特大新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學校體育館的地下有一頭白犀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.49,0:12:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年一度都會把它拉出來慶祝節日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.69,0:12:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和奏 還在睡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.87,0:12:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和奏會睡懶覺 還真是少見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不早點把我叫起來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.74,0:12:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你做了早餐 應該說謝謝才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.81,0:12:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便記得喂小虎早飯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.56,0:12:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說「拜託你了 爸爸」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.26,0:12:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了 父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.80,0:12:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 阪井杉又送了我一張票
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也和爸爸去聽聽音樂劇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.99,0:12:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.02,0:13:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和朋友一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.23,0:13:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幫我問問能不能再弄張票
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.07,0:13:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.64,0:13:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.77,0:13:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 便當拿著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經幫你做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.39,0:13:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.17,0:13:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？ 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？ 紗羽就吃這些？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？ 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.61,0:13:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前吃過便當了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.31,0:13:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子不太餓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛遮遮掩掩的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 愛心標記
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.77,0:13:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天睡過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.11,0:13:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸不知哪根筋搭錯了竟然給我做了便當
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次絕對不會讓他弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛父便當啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.67,0:13:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說不是愛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.42,0:13:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:13:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.89,0:14:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 我拿到了幾張市民音樂劇的票
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.33,0:14:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.69,0:14:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許還能為白祭找些參考
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.42,0:14:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼 要去要去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.15,0:14:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不了歌劇聽聽音樂劇也賺到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.17,0:14:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上貓咪服 唱起歌謠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似我也挺在行的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.82,0:14:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉得太兇小心又摔個底朝天哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題 船到橋頭自然直嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.25,0:14:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 紗羽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.75,0:14:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.00,0:14:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.53,0:14:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飯團也一點都沒吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.86,0:14:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天沒什麼食慾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.78,0:14:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 這個你吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.16,0:14:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.51,0:14:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在減肥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.58,0:14:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化祭上你們要準備活動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們想弄個現場音樂會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯嘛 那我來彈貝斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.71,0:14:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺她在思春麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.36,0:14:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}不過還沒找到場地 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.09,0:15:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.13,0:15:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.26,0:15:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.24,0:15:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 是關於合唱團的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.18,0:15:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們想要申請主會場舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給你負責
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.81,0:15:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.68,0:15:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部交給你來負責
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.46,0:15:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.23,0:15:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您來了呀 理事長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.49,0:15:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭候您多時了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.57,0:15:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼要緊事呢 還勞煩您今日親自跑一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的傷勢如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.77,0:15:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已無大礙 讓您費心了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.29,0:15:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒功夫擔心你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.92,0:15:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的事業計劃遇上一些阻礙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.37,0:16:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是 那個計劃已經正式定下來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.88,0:16:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要將公路計劃提前了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.97,0:16:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天來這就是為了和你談這件事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.05,0:16:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要老年生活過得衣食無憂的話 你得好好工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.14,0:16:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 能為您效勞不勝榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.72,0:16:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子有一點疼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.62,0:16:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃點藥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用 我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把軟顎打開 張大喉嚨讓聲音迴響
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.82,0:17:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好聽周圍的人的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗羽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.67,0:17:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.01,0:17:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.31,0:17:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫保健室的老師過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 先坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.60,0:17:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貧血了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.83,0:17:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.84,0:17:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的臉色很差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.53,0:17:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成你在減肥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.02,0:17:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是太勉強自己了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在減肥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.39,0:17:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就不胖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.68,0:17:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子就是太在意了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.83,0:17:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中你就閉嘴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:17:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.49,0:17:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲鈍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.17,0:17:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.84,0:17:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.44,0:17:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.07,0:17:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嘛 我也是很擔心的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我有點不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.08,0:18:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.39,0:18:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她最近有點奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.37,0:18:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺不是平時的紗羽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還是追上去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.07,0:18:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.95,0:18:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.25,0:18:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請給我一次機會 我一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.58,0:18:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅是因為喜歡不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.54,0:18:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有那種半途而廢的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.16,0:18:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那至少見個面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.94,0:19:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.61,0:19:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fall in Love（墜入愛河）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.00,0:19:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fall in Love？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.31,0:19:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.23,0:19:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.63,0:19:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她最近總是發呆 又突然開始減肥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.93,0:19:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和奏你沒有經驗可能不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.41,0:19:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是相思病啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.17,0:19:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那個電話來看對方的年紀比較大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.95,0:19:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是有婦之夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來夏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.73,0:19:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的桃色腦細胞是不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.67,0:19:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.30,0:19:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早 今天沒事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.97,0:19:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣啊 果然唱歌就是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.64,0:20:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去喝杯茶怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.78,0:20:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去 去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.27,0:20:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發現了一家感覺不錯的店
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.18,0:20:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一個人不太好意思進去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.02,0:20:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.10,0:20:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.21,0:20:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有騎射練習
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是傍晚才練習嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.86,0:20:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要帶薩布萊一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.91,0:20:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以得早點回去準備一下 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.57,0:20:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來病的不輕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.78,0:20:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一邊喝茶一邊想想對策吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.36,0:20:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.27,0:20:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前我想繞個道行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.72,0:20:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(連貓都懂的作曲教室)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.84,0:20:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作曲？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.99,0:21:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽留下了一份樂譜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.74,0:21:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是還沒有完成
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想接著寫完它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.29,0:21:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因為這是我們的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.73,0:21:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好 我也覺得身體充滿了動力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在那之前要先看看漫畫的新刊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.91,0:21:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}專區 藝大書區
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.44,0:21:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沖田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.53,0:21:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沖田同學 請出發
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.33,0:21:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.97,0:22:14.12,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴れた日雨の日でも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.22,0:22:21.08,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,みんながいれば何時も笑顔になれた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.10,0:22:26.86,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記憶の彼方まで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.15,0:22:34.53,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思い出したりたゆたう声耳に澄まそう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.68,0:22:40.72,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,さぁ　手を差し伸べられて輪の中へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.74,0:22:48.81,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一人じゃない空間で夢中になってる 時間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.18,0:22:54.56,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心地よい風が吹いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.59,0:23:01.99,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑ったり泣いたり　歌ってみたり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.36,0:23:07.68,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉じていたココロを開いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.75,0:23:14.28,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思い出のフレーズ　口ずさむ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.39,0:23:20.50,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏でよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.97,0:22:14.12,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管天晴或者下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.22,0:22:21.08,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要大家在一起 隨時都能展露笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.10,0:22:26.86,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去往記憶的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.15,0:22:34.53,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回憶往事 傾聽迴盪在耳邊的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.68,0:22:40.72,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 到伸手牽成的圓圈裏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.74,0:22:48.81,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉浸在大家的世界裏 一起度過這夢幻般的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.18,0:22:54.56,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎面吹拂著清涼的風
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.59,0:23:01.99,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們笑過 哭過 放聲高唱過
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.36,0:23:07.68,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揚起心靈的風帆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.75,0:23:14.28,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱出回憶滿滿的歌詞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.39,0:23:20.50,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起放聲高歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.94,0:23:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快叫救護車 快叫救護車
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.23,0:23:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.74,0:23:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 有人受傷了…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.66,0:23:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說當不了騎手了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.79,0:23:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱著我也行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.45,0:23:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣不行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.31,0:23:39.20,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(648,56)\3c&HCFC9C3&}第八話 時而在意 時而下定決心出發
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.62,0:23:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以放棄音樂的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就趕過去 要等著我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
